vec::Vec::<T, A>::as_mut_slice.doc:
Extracts a mutable slice of the entire vector.

Equivalent to `&mut s[..]`.

# Examples

```
use std::io::{self, Read};
let mut buffer = vec![0; 3];
io::repeat(0b101).read_exact(buffer.as_mut_slice()).unwrap();
```

